cpuType=any
description=VisualizeTfSitesOnSequences annotates transcription factor binding sites across a DNA sequence. Multiple transcription factors can be analyzed. Each binding site is labeled with a unique binding site ID and its start and end position. If reference data is provided for a transcription factor, the affinity/score of this site will be labeled and the intensity of the binding siteâ€™s color will be proportional to the affinity/score.
documentationUrl=https://genepattern.github.io/tfsites.VisualizeTFSitesOnSequences/v3/
